132
00:08:09,098 --> 00:08:12,197
Tidak. Aku akan temui dia sendiri.

133
00:08:12,198 --> 00:08:14,798
Ngomong-ngomong, Shigeko. Foto itu...

134
00:08:15,898 --> 00:08:18,797
Bisakah kau rapikan?

135
00:08:18,798 --> 00:08:23,198
Kurasa itu lima milimeter miring ke kanan.

136
00:08:25,698 --> 00:08:27,097
Hah?

137
00:08:27,098 --> 00:08:28,997
Lima milimeter?

