145
00:08:56,798 --> 00:08:59,598
Itu pintu yang aneh.

146
00:09:01,098 --> 00:09:06,598
Kau menekan kata sandinya dan tempatkan ibu jarimu di sini.

147
00:09:12,298 --> 00:09:13,797
Siapa?

148
00:09:13,798 --> 00:09:15,997
Aku Akatsuka, pelayan.

149
00:09:15,998 --> 00:09:18,997
Aku sudah membawa Detektif Mouri bersamaku.

150
00:09:18,998 --> 00:09:21,098
Aku akan langsung membuka pintunya.

151
00:09:23,498 --> 00:09:25,297
Begitu.

152
00:09:25,298 --> 00:09:27,397
Fantastis!

153
00:09:27,398 --> 00:09:28,897
